               <rs type="event" ref="#ev__QGW_II_I_1096"><rs type="fn" role="issuer"><rs type="person" ref="#pe__johann_mosprunner_QGW_II_I_1096">Hanns der Mosprunner, <roleName type="occ" corresp="#org__wien">purger</roleName> ze Wienne
                           <roleName type="rep" corresp="#pe__mosprunnerin_QGW_II_I_1096"><add>Ausrichter des
                              Geschäfts</add></roleName>
                        <roleName type="rep" corresp="#pe__katharina_mosprunnerin_QGW_II_I_1096"><add>Geschäftsherr</add></roleName></rs></rs> , <triggerstring n="disp">beurkundet</triggerstring>, dass er als Ausrichter des Geschäftes seiner <rs type="person" ref="#pe__mosprunnerin_QGW_II_I_1096"><roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__johann_mosprunner_QGW_II_I_1096">Mutter</roleName>, . . der
                     Mosprunnerinne</rs> , seiner <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs type="person" ref="#pe__katharina_mosprunnerin_QGW_II_I_1096"><roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__johann_mosprunner_QGW_II_I_1096">Schwester</roleName> Kathrem, <roleName type="occ" corresp="#org__wien-st_niklas_vor_dem_stubentor_zisterzienserinnen">Conventschwester</roleName></rs> in dem Frauenkloster dacz sand Niclas
                     vor Stubentor</rs> , zwei Fleischbänke, gelegen bei sand Michels pharrchirchen
                  ze Wienne, und ain chram, gelegen an dem Hohenmarcht bei dem Stokch ze Wienne ,
                     <triggerstring n="disp">eingeantwortet habe</triggerstring>, welche nach ihrem
                  Ableben an das <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs type="org" ref="#org__wien-st_niklas_vor_dem_stubentor_zisterzienserinnen">Kloster</rs></rs> fallen sollen.</rs>
            </p></div><div type="seal"><p><rs type="event" ref="#ev__QGW_II_I_1096"><rs type="fn" role="witness">Besiegelt mit
                     den Siegeln: 1. seines <rs type="person" ref="#pe__konrad_rokk_QGW_II_I_1031"><roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__johann_mosprunner_QGW_II_I_1096">Schwagers</roleName>
                        <roleName type="title">hern</roleName> Chunrats des Rokken <roleName type="occ" corresp="#org__wien"><add>Ratsherr</add></roleName></rs>, 2.
                        <rs type="person" ref="#pe__friedrich_dietram_QGW_II_I_1026"><roleName type="title">hern</roleName> Fridreichs des Dietrams, baide <roleName type="occ" corresp="#org__wien">des rats der stat ze
                  Wienne</roleName></rs>.</rs></rs>
            </p></div><div type="nota"><p/></div><div type="lists"><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/placeList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/personList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/eventList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/orgList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/></div></body></text></TEI>